{"id":582639873,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1636145998,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"128 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/582639873/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"44.5 MB","code":"/**\n * @param {string} s\n * @return {number}\n */\nvar lengthOfLongestSubstring = function(s) {\n    let map = {}, j = 0, max = 0\n    \n    for (let i = 0; i < s.length; i++) {\n        // if the map already contains the 's[i]', shrink the window from the beginning so that\n        // we have only one occurrence of 's[i]'\n        if (s[i] in map) {\n            j = Math.max(j, map[s[i]] + 1)\n        }\n        map[s[i]] = i\n        \n        max = Math.max(max, i - j + 1)\n    }\n    return max\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false}
